 />\ntears in my heart <br />\ntrees<br />\ngoner <br />\nfairly local<br />\nguns for hand <br />\nheavydirtysoul <br />\nlane boy<br />\nthe judge<br />\nmigraine <br />\ncancer <br />\na car, a torch, a death <br />\nride<br />\n呢幾首特別印象深刻<br />\n<br />\ngoner 個風格真係好正 最尾個下爆發 感情爆曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同LP既the messengers 有d接近個風格 兩首都好鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntears in my heart 既輕快節奏令人腦中不斷響起個melody <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nride 個節奏比較岩大眾口味 亦十分好聽<br />\n<br />\n太多講唔曬 上面個幾首係必聽推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係car radio 真係未聽過全rap歌可以好聽到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ntop既歌真係好正 一首歌入邊可以聽到幾種不同風格 <br />\nd就爆就爆既嘶吼令人唔會厭<br />\n真係好有才華<br />\n好希望可以現場睇佢地既live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔小心打太多<br />\n希望可以有更多人聰呢隊band <br />\n但佢地係香港仲未紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a68104b256c782c25af6300efaba2ce9af0710","tid":55381,"uid":30533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T07:25:30.000Z","msg":"聽過live就更加返唔到轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49755e31d51a6873d5292343badb26139086a141","tid":55381,"uid":51275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽過live就更加返唔到轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打睇過現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"9905a8d8d8ce4d7bf8be99b606c5b4663158c8b2","tid":55381,"uid":30533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply